    "description": "<p>Our company specializes in precision manufacturing and modular assembly for global high-end industries. With additional operations in Malaysia and China, we deliver reliable and scalable solutions to international clients.<br /><br />Our core expertise covers MedTech, Aerospace, and Semiconductor sectors. We provide end-to-end services ranging from structural components machining, sheet metal fabrication, to full-system integration and OEM/ODM solutions. Over the years, we have built strong partnerships with leading global clients, recognized for our commitment to consistent quality, on-time delivery, and cross-border collaboration.<br /></p><p>Location: 1 N Buona Vista Link, Elementum, Singapore 139691<br />LinkedIn Page: https://www.linkedin.com/company/brigo-technology-singapore-pte-ltd/about/</p>",
